Kita akan menabrak.

101
00:08:10,050 --> 00:08:11,070
Gawat!

102
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:12,300
Maju terus!

103
00:08:12,990 --> 00:08:14,810
Semuanya, berpeganglah!

104
00:08:16,030 --> 00:08:17,240
Apa yang kamu inginkan?

105
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,450
Terbang!

106
00:08:24,570 --> 00:08:26,120
Terbang?

107
