113
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:40,909
Jika tetap terbang, itu akan bagus.

114
00:08:41,789 --> 00:08:43,570
Kapten, kita akan turun di mana?

115
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:45,340
Oh ya, kita akan turun di mana?

116
00:08:45,420 --> 00:08:47,070
Jangan bercanda!

117
