Hei, lihatlah ke sini!

166
00:13:51,090 --> 00:13:52,520
Mengapa dia kabur?

167
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:56,020
Orang pasti terkejut
melihat bendera bajak laut...

168
00:13:56,700 --> 00:13:57,590
Kalau gitu...

169
00:13:58,970 --> 00:14:01,190
- Tunggu aku, Luffy.
- Luffy, Usopp.

170
