178
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:29,280
Terlihat.

179
00:14:29,430 --> 00:14:31,620
Tunggu...
aku ingin bertanya padamu.

180
00:14:34,740 --> 00:14:36,560
Nona, jangan takut!

181
00:14:36,640 --> 00:14:38,720
Kami bukan orang aneh.

182
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:41,560
Apakah orang sepertimu tidak aneh?

183
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:43,300
Nami, jangan begitu.

184
00:14:49,650 --> 00:14:51,510
Berikan namamu dong!

185
00:14:52,020 --> 00:14:54,240
