Siap.

206
00:15:57,620 --> 00:16:00,170
Nona Maya, kumohon Anda menjaga Nenek.

207
00:16:00,690 --> 00:16:02,550
Bagaimana bajak laut bisa datang?

208
00:16:02,690 --> 00:16:03,910
Aduh, bagaimana ini?

209
