215
00:16:14,140 --> 00:16:15,190
Cepat sembunyikan!

216
00:16:16,710 --> 00:16:17,560
Cepatlah!

217
00:16:18,010 --> 00:16:18,930
Di sini...

218
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,190
Sini...

219
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:21,130
Cepat!

220
00:16:21,280 --> 00:16:21,760
Sembunyikan!

221
00:16:21,850 --> 00:16:22,820
Cepat sembunyikan!

222
00:16:23,010 --> 00:16:25,770
Kami mohon para perempuan menjaga anak-anak.

223
00:16:26,150 --> 00:16:27,940
- Jalan!
- Kalian pergilah ke timur.

224
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:29,440
Siap.

225
00:16:29,590 --> 00:16:32,270
Tidak boleh mengulangi tragedi buruk itu lagi.

226
00:16:32,460 --> 00:16:33,640
Tidak boleh!

227
00:16:34,220 --> 00:16:35,770
Nenek, cepatlah bersembunyi!

228
00:16:35,860 --> 00:16:38,340
Tidak, aku harus menjaga tempat ini.

229
00:16:38,530 --> 00:16:39,010
Namun...

230
00:16:39,160 --> 00:16:39,950
Halo semuanya.

231
00:16:41,030 --> 00:16:41,780
Bajak laut.

232
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:43,950
