287
00:19:18,690 --> 00:19:19,870
Pusaka?

288
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:21,380
Maya.

289
00:19:23,130 --> 00:19:24,520
Kuserahkan pada kalian!

290
00:19:26,830 --> 00:19:27,440
Zoro.

291
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:30,190
Apakah bajingan itu...

292
00:19:30,530 --> 00:19:31,460
Sanji.

293
00:19:39,780 --> 00:19:40,530
Nenek...

294
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:41,530
Berhenti!

295
00:19:43,050 --> 00:19:45,200
