313
00:20:41,340 --> 00:20:43,090
Mengapa kau berbuat ini, Zoro?

314
00:20:43,170 --> 00:20:46,030
Keterlaluan.
Apa salah Sanji padamu?

315
00:20:47,110 --> 00:20:49,590
Nenek, Nona Maya.

316
00:20:50,210 --> 00:20:51,830
Maya, cepatlah kabur!

317
00:21:02,490 --> 00:21:03,350
Zoro.

318
00:21:03,730 --> 00:21:04,770
Nona Maya.

319
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:16,930
Kubawa ini.

320
00:21:17,570 --> 00:21:18,220
Kembalikan!

321
00:21:18,370 --> 00:21:20,990
Itu adalah harta yang berharga bagi kami.

322
00:21:21,080 --> 00:21:22,230
Ini juga berharga bagiku.

323
00:21:22,710 --> 00:21:24,930
Sudah cukup, simpanlah semua pedang!

324
00:21:25,080 --> 00:21:25,560
Pulau ini,

325
