353
00:22:50,670 --> 00:22:52,210
Cepat tinggalkan tempat ini, Luffy.

354
00:22:53,900 --> 00:22:55,220
Apakah kalian melihat Zoro?

355
00:22:55,300 --> 00:22:57,020
Zoro... Wah bahaya!

356
00:22:57,110 --> 00:23:00,830
Zoro...

357
00:23:00,980 --> 00:23:02,300
Luffy si Topi Jerami.

358
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:05,960
Apakah kamu melihat Zoro?

359
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:09,230
Tuan Zoro, dia akan segera kembali.

360
00:23:09,350 --> 00:23:12,470
Benarkah?
Jadi, kami menunggu dia di sini.

361
00:23:12,560 --> 00:23:13,980
Usopp, ini sungguh bagus.

362
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:15,740
Kita akhirnya menemukan Zoro.

363
00:23:15,830 --> 00:23:18,340
Mengapa Zoro ada di Dojo Marine?

364
00:23:18,490 --> 00:23:19,750
Aku tak peduli.

365
00:23:19,860 --> 00:23:22,120
Yang penting Zoro bisa kembali, ya 'kan?

366
00:23:22,270 --> 00:23:23,240
Ya.

367
00:23:32,070 --> 00:23:34,860
Apakah kau buronan 100 juta?

368
00:23:35,010 --> 00:23:36,370
Ya, benar.

369
00:23:36,850 --> 00:23:38,200
Kau mirip seperti pendekar.

370
00:23:38,280 --> 00:23:39,330
Bukan hanya mirip,

371
00:23:39,450 --> 00:23:42,340
