386
00:24:33,180 --> 00:24:34,960
Sudah lama aku tidak merasa bersemangat.

387
00:24:36,180 --> 00:24:37,030
Permainan berakhir.

388
00:24:37,110 --> 00:24:37,970
Apa?

389
00:24:38,780 --> 00:24:41,100
Zoro sudah tidak perlu bertemu kalian.

390
00:24:41,220 --> 00:24:44,670
Karena dia bukan rekan bajak laut kalian lagi.

391
00:24:47,420 --> 00:24:49,180
Omong kosong apa itu?

392
00:24:49,290 --> 00:24:50,110
Luffy.

393
00:24:50,690 --> 00:24:52,340
Touma, mundurlah!

394
00:24:52,430 --> 00:24:53,180
Ya.

395
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:01,350
Ingin bertarung?

396
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:06,130
Baiklah, terimalah!

397
00:25:06,210 --> 00:25:08,790
Gomu-Gomu no Pistol.

398
00:25:10,380 --> 00:25:13,500
Gomu-Gomu no Muchi.

399
00:25:15,150 --> 00:25:16,510
Hebat, Luffy.

400
00:25:17,390 --> 00:25:18,370
Maaf...

401
00:25:18,520 --> 00:25:20,240
Harusnya semua menghindar.

402
00:25:25,030 --> 00:25:25,950
Terimalah!

403
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:28,090
Datanglah!

404
00:25:41,280 --> 00:25:43,390
Apa itu?
Aneh sekali.

405
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:45,530
Pedang yang aneh.

406
00:25:45,610 --> 00:25:47,970
Kuberi tahu, aku membencimu.

407
00:25:48,120 --> 00:25:50,170
Apakah kau tahu kekuatan apa ini?

408
00:25:50,290 --> 00:25:52,340
Apakah kau pernah mendengar suara ini?

409
00:25:54,620 --> 00:25:56,600
Aku ingin darah segarmu.

410
00:26:10,510 --> 00:26:11,490
Tidak mungkin...

411
00:26:12,210 --> 00:26:12,930
Sakit...

412
00:26:15,950 --> 00:26:16,700
Gomu-Gomu no...

413
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:18,630
Stomp, Kama, Pistol.

414
00:26:23,150 --> 00:26:24,630
Ayo semangat, Luffy!

415
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:27,010
Luffy seharusnya adalah pemakan buah setan.

416
00:26:27,820 --> 00:26:29,370
Kemampuannya sungguh unik.

417
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:31,580
Bukan hanya unik,

418
00:26:31,660 --> 00:26:33,020
