Sungguh konyol.

426
00:26:57,820 --> 00:27:00,680
Kau sama dengan bajak laut yang lain.

427
00:27:00,760 --> 00:27:03,980
Tak sama.
Aku ingin menjadi raja bajak laut.

428
00:27:04,830 --> 00:27:05,810
Raja bajak laut?

429
00:27:05,930 --> 00:27:08,110
Bagus sekali, Kapten!

430
00:27:08,260 --> 00:27:09,240
Sangat membosankan.

431
00:27:09,330 --> 00:27:11,850
