Luka kecil ini tidak berarti.

466
00:29:39,980 --> 00:29:41,270
Bagaimana dengan lukamu?

467
00:29:41,420 --> 00:29:42,470
Tak perlu khawatir.

468
00:29:44,720 --> 00:29:45,770
Dokter, tolonglah saya!

469
00:29:45,850 --> 00:29:47,470
Aku masih membutuhkan obat di sini.

470
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:49,140
Oke, tak apa-apa,

471
00:29:49,220 --> 00:29:50,480
